  m_text: "\nMax permanence:\n\r\nthis is how much time at most you can make your
    clients stay on the planet because of\r\npolitical or weather problems, also
    our policy doesn\u2019t cover more than that time for each\r\nplanet.\n\r\nlevels
    of max permanence:\n\r\ndays\n\r\nmonths\n\r\nyears\r\n"
